{"tid":854812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：馬凱被拒發簽證　與觸及「港獨」底線有關","createTime":"2018-10-09T15:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T17:52:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"97421a624345ced1b755c37dd961248d0916c64e","tid":854812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1422071-20181009.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1422071-20181009.htm&d=9muGD2B2HDW9YKzsh4glQfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7403e324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1422071-20181009.htm&h=d9ddb9c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1422071-20181009.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1422071_1_L_20181009195245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1422071_1_L_20181009195245.jpg&h=723bfa20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港外國記者會副主席馬凱，不獲特區政府續發工作簽證。據了解，馬凱被拒續發簽證，與觸及「港獨」的底線有關，又指日後凡涉及「港獨」議題，政府都會果斷處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，政府是否向外國人發出簽證，一般情況下，除了會考慮申請人有沒有不良紀錄，例如犯罪行為，亦會考慮申請人是否有做過任何對本港不利的事。消息人士舉例，美國也不會向申請入境人士，解釋拒絕發出簽證的原因。<br />\n<br />\n至於外國記者會會址續租問題，據了解，租約尚有數年才到期，消息人士表示，至今未聽聞要採取任何行動。"},{"pid":"b34f886964e40ef17dc6558e2ff7d5fced7387cf","tid":854812,"uid":190540,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f36f71d3da234be2bed4ac76eb57b6ebf303380f","tid":854812,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"old news.."},{"pid":"ed7078db59e897212366f593a5b28a0b83579ef7","tid":854812,"uid":8000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"唔使消息 係人都知啦下話"},{"pid":"21a079e4d4a9f2f86842cb88fcf33713da630c11","tid":854812,"uid":67771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"